Class Ecommerce.Employee

java.lang.Object
Ecommerce.People
Ecommerce.Customer
Ecommerce.Employee
Enclosing class:
Ecommerce
public class Ecommerce.Employee
extends Ecommerce.Customer
The Employee class is an extension of class Customer. An employee can access all the methods contained in Customer, but it also can send the orders of the clients and restock the storage.

Ecommerce.Customer, Ecommerce.People, Ecommerce
